&lt;p&gt;North Tyneside CAMHS has an exciting opportunity to appoint a Band 6 Registered Nurse as a CAMHS mental health worker within the service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a fantastic opportunity to join us at a time when the service is reviewing and developing its model of delivery.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will join a multi disciplinary team made up of Nurses, Psychiatrists, Clinical Psychologists and Specialist Mental health Therapists.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a dynamic and motivated individual with excellent clinical skills. The successful candidate will be pivotal to support the development of the specialist service and in return work as part of a small and cohesive team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For an informal chat or visit please contact - Rhu Liddle - rhianna.liddle@northumbria-healthcare.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name: Rhu Liddle&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title: Senior CAMHS Practitioner&lt;/p&gt;
